
Custom Resource Definition  - CRD 

...............flightticket.yml........

apiVersion: flights.com/v1
kind: FlightTicket
metadata:
  name: my-flight-ticket 

spec:
  from: Mumbai
  to: London
  number: 2

...............

Custom Resource ---- >ETCD  ---> Custom Controller ...Monitor, Change 


kubectl create -f flightticket.yml 

kubectl get flightticket


For custom resources we need to have custom controller 




Custom Controller :
-------------------
    uses Go language 



Operator Framework:
-------------------

Customer resource definition (CRD) and Custom Controller (CC)

These two CRD and CC can be deployed as single entity using Operator Framework

k create -f flight-operator.yaml 


OperatorHub.io 
